<div id="wb_element_instance726" class="wb_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"><strong><font color="#e3b709">USHUAIA</font></strong></h3>

<p> </p>

<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Ushuaia is the capital of the Province of Tierra del Fuego, Antarctica and South Atlantic Islands. It was founded on October 12, 1884 by Augusto Lasserre and is located on the shores of the Beagle Channel surrounded by the Martial mountain range, in the Bay of Ushuaia. Besides being an administrative center, it is an industrial, port and tourist knot. Ushuaia is known as the southernmost city in the world.</strong></h1>

<h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"> </h3>

<h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>USHUAIA 4 days, 3 nights</strong></h3>

