<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong>*</strong><strong>Transfers Airport/ Hotel/ Airport.<br>
* 3 nights lodging with breakfast.<br>
* Excursion: Tierra del Fuego National Park +Train to The End of the World<br>
* Golf Day</strong></h1>

<p> </p>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Day 1: BUENOS AIRES / USHUAIA</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><br><strong>Transfer to the airport of Buenos Aires. You will head for "The End of the World" and will arrive in the southernmost city that you ever visit. Transfer to the selected hotel. The rest of the day is free. Night at the hotel.</strong><br>
 </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Day 2: USHUAIA</strong></h2>

<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1"><strong>BREAKFAST AND DEPARTURE FOR THE TIERRA DEL FUEGO NATIONAL PARK + TRAIN TO THE END OF THE WORLD. THERE YOU COULD SEE NATURE AT ITS BEST. AND IF YOU WANT TO BE MORE ADVENTUROUS YOU COULD ENJOY THE PARK THE WHOLE DAY. AND DON'T GET DESPERATE, TOMORROW YOU WILL HAVE MANY THINGS TO DO.<br>
LODGING.</strong></h1>

